## **7) Trigger Keywords: OLD vs NEW**

| Keyword | Used In        | Meaning                 |
| ------- | -------------- | ----------------------- |
| **NEW** | INSERT, UPDATE | The new row values      |
| **OLD** | UPDATE, DELETE | The previous row values |

Examples:

* `NEW.name` â†’ value being inserted/updated
* `OLD.name` â†’ value before update or before delete

